252
00:29:03,150 --> 00:29:05,234
Now those days are gone!

253
00:29:05,435 --> 00:29:10,233
Now don’t doubt yourself and just go
full ahead

254
00:29:10,434 --> 00:29:15,932
with all the maryadas of Sahaja Yoga.
