261
00:29:50,826 --> 00:29:54,485
such a person that you do not become
obnoxious,

262
00:29:54,686 --> 00:29:59,422
or people don’t think you are queer,
strange people.

263
00:29:59,623 --> 00:30:02,900
To overcome that, we have to dress up
in a way

264
00:30:03,101 --> 00:30:07,596
that is rather more appealing to
